{"tid":726413,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去旅行大家有無試過遇到啲靈異事件？（2）","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T16:03:46.000Z","uid":83934,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"8187d959afefa576322608c88853fdefc6499b6d","tid":726413,"uid":83934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思大家 由於小弟無時間做酒店整合 但一有時間就會整<br />\n上一個post我敢講 靈異王一定係#22 個位巴打同佢女朋友去旅行嘅時候發現 係無買同帶dum嘅情況下 竟然佢女朋友個袋出現咗個佢地用開嘅牌子dum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當時睇到驚撚到仆街<br />\n好 如對之前巴打們講嘅靈異事件有興趣又想避啲恐怖酒店 請移玉步到上個po<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/711060/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/711060/page/1</a><br />\n重申一點 信不信由你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家互相專重就好 <br />\n廢話少講 大家請繼續分享"},{"pid":"1ff81731c730e67aef9cca54c1459083c8b22bf8","tid":726413,"uid":83934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf328531ebeec8f68b87b71d7740fdc3617f7f1","tid":726413,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e53904d18c0f2289e67876d76ae5bb7a494155","tid":726413,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"有鬼"},{"pid":"d751f470137e32e3faf3099a6163ec956f5d3145","tid":726413,"uid":92643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma